<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<h3>How much does exterior painting cost in Askern?</h3>
<p>Most DN6 homes range between <strong>£250–£1,200</strong> depending on property size and preparation required. We always provide a free, no-obligation quote.</p>

<h3>Do you prepare surfaces before painting?</h3>
<p>Yes, all surfaces are cleaned, sanded, scraped, and primed for a professional, long-lasting finish.</p>

<h3>Which paints do you use for exterior projects?</h3>
<p>We use premium-quality exterior paints, including Sandtex masonry paint for walls and specialist wood coatings for fences, gates, and sheds.</p>

<h3>Is your work insured?</h3>
<p>Yes, all exterior decorating and painting work is fully insured for peace of mind.</p>

